title: I WILL CALL UPON THE LORD
verses: I will call upon the Lord,=Who is worthy to be praised:=I will call upon the Lord,=Who is worthy to be praised:=So shall I be saved from mine enemies.=The Lord reigneth; blessed be the Lord=Let the Rock of my salvation be exalted.=The Lord reigneth; blessed be the Lord=Let the Rock of my salvation be exalted.
